<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>207</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Árdaıym qýanyp júrińder shattanyp,
 Júrek syryn Táńirge birge aqtaryp.
 Baqytty bolaıyq otyrǵan bárimiz,
 Kókke jetsin birigip salǵan ánimiz.

[C1]
   Jumaqtyń gúlin tereıik,
   Shyn júrekten Isaǵa keleıik.
   Jumaq kilti tek Sonyń qolynda,
   Júreıik kúmánsiz sońynda.

[V2]
 Bir-birińdi uǵynyp syılap ótińder,
 Jumaqqa qol ustasyp birge jetińder.
 Súıispenshilikteriń shynaıy bolsyn,
 Bastaryńa ketpeıtindeı baqyt qonsyn.

[V3]
 Qutty bolsyn bas qosqan osy toılaryń,
 Birge bolsyn bar kezde arman, oılaryń.
 Sát sapar tileımiz, oń bolsyn joldaryń,
 Jazylmasyn myqty ustaǵan qoldaryń.</lyrics>
<title>Árdaıym qýanyp júrińder shattanyp РӘЖ207</title>
</song>